                    <ul>
                        <li>Cancer is a disease in which abnormal cells divide uncontrollably and destroy body tissue.</li>
                        <br>
                        <li>The most common cancers of children are Leukemia, Bone tumors, brain tumors, and Hodgkins lymphoma.</li>
                        <br>
                        <li>Sickle cell is a group of inherited red blood cell disorders.</li>
                        <br> 
                        <li>They cause red blood cells to become misshapen and break down.</li> 
